text: Ok changing to 5 stars not because of the durian but it's their after sales and service recovery service is top notch. The initial 3 boxes i got yesterday were of inferior quality and today after a quick call, they decided to send 3 new boxes to me. I won't say it's the best dream lover i tried, and their durian are on the smaller side, it's still very good. All 6 boxes were ranging 440gm to 495gm. Thumbs up.

Good durian seller are really hard to find.

Their MSW really up to standard.

Will go to them for my future purchases.
